General.Name: Icetana Ltd
General.Description: iCetana Limited, a Software as a Service software company, provides video analytics solutions in the Asia Pacific, North America, Europe, the Middle East, and Africa. The company engages in the development and commercialization of iCetana Solution, an AI-assisted video surveillance software to provide automated real-time anomalous event detection. It serves various industries, including prisons, healthcare, and guarding services. The company was founded in 2009 and is based in Perth, Australia.
